== 體育和運動 ==
埃及在[[全非運動會|全非運動會]]上常常有傑出的表現，往往不是第一就是第二，在非洲體壇的領導地位突出。

[[足球|足球]]是埃及最受欢迎的运动，自[[非洲国家杯|非洲国家杯]]成立以来，埃及共夺得7次冠军，为所有非洲国家之最。

在所有的[[非洲國家和地區列表|非洲國家及地區]]中，埃及國家籃球隊在[[世界盃籃球賽|世界盃籃球賽]]和[[夏季奧林匹克運動會籃球比賽|夏季奥运]]<ref>{{cite web | url=http://archive.fiba.com/pages/eng/fa/event/p/cid//sid/2902/_/1950_FIBA_World_Championship_for_Men/index.html | title=1950 World Championship for Men | publisher=FIBA | date=9 June 2012 | accessdate=9 June 2012 | archive-date=2012-11-13 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121113212042/http://archive.fiba.com/pages/eng/fa/event/p/cid//sid/2902/_/1950_FIBA_World_Championship_for_Men/index.html | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=http://archive.fiba.com/pages/eng/fa/team/p/sid/2933/tid/276/_/1952_Olympic_Games_Tournament_for_Men/index.html | title=Egypt – 1952 Olympic Games; Tournament for Men | publisher=FIBA | date=9 June 2012 | accessdate=9 June 2012 | archive-date=2012-08-11 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120811212844/http://archive.fiba.com/pages/eng/fa/team/p/sid/2933/tid/276/_/1952_Olympic_Games_Tournament_for_Men/index.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>上保持著最佳成績記錄。

